INSTALL
-------------------------

1. Put "FY_RumblStube_TWS.bsp", "FY_RumblStube_TWS.nav" and "FY_RumblStube_TWS.txt" here:
   "C:\Programs\Steam\SteamApps\1245780\counter-strike source\cstrike\maps"

2. Start up Counter-Strike: Source and play FY_RumblStube !
